"></path></svg></a>Newsletters</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.grantfortheweb.org/signup\">Newsletter of grantfortheweb.org</a> - Sign up for email updates.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/jkga/is-web-monetized\">Is web monetized</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jkga/is-web-monetized\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - A very simple tool for checking if Web Monetization is enabled.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sorxrob/paytrackr\">Paytrackr</a> - Track and manage your micropayments into one place.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PayTrackr is the easiest and safest way to track and manage your micropayments to web monetized websites, having a web monetization provider membership.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/esse-dev/akita\">Akita</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/esse-dev/akita\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">21</span></span></a> - A browser extension that gives you insight into your involvement with Web Monetization.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Akita presents your top visited monetized sites, how much time you're spending on them, and how much you're contributing (or could contribute) to them.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/signalnerve/openmonetizationwallet\">Open Monetization Wallet</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/signalnerve/openmonetizationwallet\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">13</span></span></a> - Tools for managing your vanity Web Monetization wallet.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Open Monetization Wallet (OMW) makes it easier to accept payments with the Web Monetization API at scale. Some features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Custom wallet URLs: own your own \"Payment Pointer\", e.g. $wallet.signalnerve.com, instead of $pay.stronghold.co/abcdef123</li>\n<li>Change between wallets/providers with no downtime</li>\n<li>Logs of incoming payment requests</li>\n<li>Revenue sharing between multiple wallets, e.g. for multiple team members</li>\n<li>Infinitely scalable with serverless technology</li>\n<li>Free and open-source</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://community.interledger.org/\">Web Monetization Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/GrantForTheWeb\">@GrantForTheWeb on Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Coil\">@Coil on Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CinnamonVideo\">@CinnamonVideo on Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev.to/t/webmonetization\">Web Monetization tag on DEV</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"contribute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contribute\" aria-label=\"contribute permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contribute</h2>\n<p>Contributions welcome ! Read the <a href=\"https://github.com/thomasbnt/awesome-web-monetization/blob/main/contributing.md\">contribution guidelines</a> first.\nYou can also contribute to share this repository and Web Monetization with your friends. 😄</p>\n<p>If you want add a new small icon, the height must be <strong>16px</strong>. Put in <code class=\"language-text\">assets/small_icons/NAME.png</code>. Format PNG only accepted.</p>\n<h2 id=\"donate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#donate\" aria-label=\"donate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Donate</h2>\n<p>Feel free to help <a href=\"https://github.com/thomasbnt\">me</a> for the maintenance of this project !\nThanks to all <strong>Sponsors on GitHub</strong> !</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/thomasbnt\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thomasbnt/sponsors@1.0/sponsors.svg\" alt=\"Github Sponsors\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/thomasbnt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Sponsor%20me-%23EA54AE.svg?&#x26;style=for-the-badge&#x26;logo=github-sponsors&#x26;logoColor=white\" alt=\"GitHub Sponsors\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/thomasbnt?via=thomasbnt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support%20me-on%20Buy%20Me%20a%20Coffee-%23FFDD00?style=for-the-badge&#x26;logo=buy-me-a-coffee&#x26;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Buy Me a Coffee\"></a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#awesome-web-monetization-awesome\">Awesome Web Monetization <img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge-flat2.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#contents\">Contents</a></p>\n</li>\n